replies.body:
It is far from an assassin meta.

But, Katarina is a very reliable assassin right now. I recommend her if you are willing to sink in more hours to learn her.

MF is good bot lane. She is probably more reliable than kat, and a lower skill floor. I can easily pick her up and do well with her without learning all of the 'tricks' that MF mains have. her only bane are high mobility cc champions and this butt {{champion:157}}
